ransition back into work?</p><p class="SupAnswer"><strong>Hon BILL ENGLISH</strong>: I hope that the person he is referring to gets the best treatment and gets a path back to work. That is one of the purposes of ACC. But I cannot comment on the individual case.</p></div></body>
